Package com.datastructures.Managers

Class UserManager

java.lang.Object
com.datastructures.Managers.UserManager
public class UserManager
extends java.lang.Object
This class deals with all user related actions throughout the app. This includes login and sign up actions as well.

Biruk Mengistu, Mya Hartman, Elena Lam
